    • Constructor Detail

      • IntakeSubsystem

        public IntakeSubsystem()
        Initialize the subsystem by creating the motor controller and solenoids up, the intake motor is inverted by default to suck in. Initializes the WPI_VictorSPX and Double Solenoid.
